{
  "_comment": [
    "JSON-LD SoftwareApplication Schema — embed on your product/pricing page.",
    "This schema tells Google your product is a software application with pricing and reviews.",
    "It can power rich results showing star ratings and price in search results.",
    "",
    "When to use: Add to your main product page and/or pricing page.",
    "Validate: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results",
    "Docs: https://schema.org/SoftwareApplication",
    "",
    "[CUSTOMIZE] Replace ALL values below with your actual product information.",
    "Remove the _comment field before embedding in production.",
    "Companion tools: coreyhaines31/marketingskills -> seo-audit"
  ],

